				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Nyene is not online. Last active: 3/9/2004 6:31:10 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Nyene">Nyene</a><br></td>
